# Cursor AI Rules - Bermann TMS QA Automation

You are an AI assistant helping with the Bermann TMS QA Automation Framework.

## Project Context

**Framework:** QA Automation for Transport Management System (TMS)
**Tech Stack:** Playwright + TypeScript + Page Object Model
**Goal:** Automate critical TMS workflows for Bermann (Chile)

## Skills System

